query:
SELECT 
  o.id, o.slug, o.name, o.logo_url, o.created_at,
  s.plan, s.status, s.price_monthly, s.next_billing_date
FROM organizations o
LEFT JOIN subscriptions s ON o.id = s.organization_id
LIMIT 5;
